        {
            "title": "警葵涌工廈搗毒品儲存倉檢值81萬元K仔 拘48歲男涉販毒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"被捕人士帶署調查。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a5a6e735c6d90c56c8a4e3b3ad271f1a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040914030518263.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">被捕人士帶署調查。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>葵青警區特別職務隊人員於昨日（8日）在葵涌葵定路一帶進行反毒品行動，並於一工業大廈搗破一個懷疑毒品儲存倉庫。人員在該工廈地面截查一名形跡可疑的男子，其後搜查其單位，在單位內檢獲約1.7公斤懷疑氯胺酮，檢獲的毒品市值約81萬元。該名48歲姓章本地男子涉嫌「販運危險藥物」被捕，現正被扣留調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185269/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示檢獲的毒品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebc092e13f64dfd205755b13b1fddd74/2025-04/MIU_Trafficking_in_DD_KWTDIST_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示檢獲的毒品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n警方重申，販運危險藥物屬嚴重罪行，根據香港法例第134章《危險藥物條例》，任何人販運危險藥物，一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款五百萬元及終身監禁，市民切勿以身試法。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062976/即時-港聞-警葵涌工廈搗毒品儲存倉檢值81萬元K仔-拘48歲男涉販毒",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 14:11:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐聯｜阿仙奴贏波益聯賽對手 英超落實下季獲5席歐聯 最多更可有7隊參賽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/afb3976a821f8392742f771dbd302be4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040913275933961.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>隨著阿仙奴於周二歐聯8強首回合主場3:0大炒皇家馬德里後，英超今季的歐戰系數已鎖定頭二，故落實下季可獲1個額外歐聯資格，換言之聯賽頭5都可參加歐聯，對前五邊緣球隊包括曼城是天大喜訊。此外，在最極端的情況下，英超下季最多更可有7隊參加歐聯。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d03c0add9ae1426fb9894894a27798c7/2025-04/AFP__20250408__39LE6F6__v1__HighRes__FblEngC1ArsenalRealMadrid_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/56a0191d6b7518034805312ce71981e3/2025-04/AFP__20250408__bretonhernandez-arsenalf250408_npx0w__v1__HighRes__ArsenalFcVRealMadr_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴贏波令英超落實下季獲5席歐聯。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c095e8b690cc8f4b76d27978ec0eab30/2025-04/AFP__20250402__38VR2FW__v1__HighRes__FblEngPrManCityLeicester.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9889488cb70744c6619ae4bbb4d0490c/2025-04/AFP__20250406__39BR9DN__v2__HighRes__FblEngPrManUtdManCity.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5cd2283e4d9cbe55f99c8d30b40c6b4f/2025-04/AFP__20250406__39B43HM__v1__HighRes__FblEngPrBrentfordChelsea.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ca12f649ea8d60f2e1aade768106adf9/2025-04/AFP__20250406__39B92MY__v1__HighRes__FblEngPrBrentfordChelsea.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士正爭取下季歐聯席位。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>英超落實下季獲5席歐聯</h2>\n<p>一眾英超球隊今季在三線歐洲賽都有不錯的表現，故英超今季的歐戰系數一直領先其他國家。未計周二的歐聯賽果，英超球隊只要多取1勝或2和，即可為英超鎖定今季歐戰系數頭二，最終阿仙奴成功擊敗皇馬，為英超爭取到下季多一個歐聯席位。\n\n</p><h2>前五形勢緊湊</h2>\n<p>這代表英超今季的前五名將可獲下季歐聯資格。而目前前五競爭激烈，第4位的車路士與第8位的富咸只有5分差距，在尚餘7輪下，排名仍有很多變數。\n\n</p><h2>最多可7隊踢歐聯</h2>\n<p>而如果阿士東維拉贏得歐聯冠軍，但最終未能打入英超頭五，屆時頭五名加維拉將可出戰歐聯。若同時間曼聯或熱刺贏得歐霸冠軍，他們亦可以歐霸冠軍身分出戰歐聯，令英超下季最多可有7隊踢歐聯。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062972/即時-體育-歐聯-阿仙奴贏波益聯賽對手-英超落實下季獲5席歐聯-最多更可有7隊參賽",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-09 14:11:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大角咀中英樓單位塌石屎天花 女戶主「中頭獎」淌血送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"單位塌石屎天花擊中女戶主。讀者提供\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/dbd305472af373cdc7ad198ab6191a5e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040913474992671.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">單位塌石屎天花擊中女戶主。讀者提供</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大角咀道163號中英樓一單位，今(9日)早上11時53分，女戶主報案指，屋內天花板突墮下多塊石屎，面積約1米乘1米，當時她在家中看電視，被墮下石屎擊中頭部，當場淌血，幸她仍然清醒，可自行報警求助。救護員接報到場，為她包紮後，將她送院敷治。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"none-100\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185245/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位內塌石屎天花，鋼筋外露。讀者提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae9b140ff670cf8adf81c8e8898edd45/2025-04/3_3_7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位內塌石屎天花，鋼筋外露。讀者提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"none-100\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185246/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地面滿佈石屎碎。讀者提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/465beb4340d71505da3144a0f1cb5ca3/2025-04/4_3_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地面滿佈石屎碎。讀者提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185242/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b71b67f1c06149795fbeae3e2d2bef54/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_132929073.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185243/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64697115c50006d93e4f83a5c0752579/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_132929073_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185244/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"屋宇署、消防及警方在塌石屎單位對上一層即天台檢查地面及結構安全。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68899744359108b72644d90a99efb02b/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_133022071.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        屋宇署、消防及警方在塌石屎單位對上一層即天台檢查地面及結構安全。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>從讀者提供的圖片可見，單位天花石屎剝落，面積約1米乘1米，天花部分鋼筋外露，而屋內地面及家具滿佈石屎碎，有部分石屎較大塊。屋宇署、消防及警方在塌石屎單位對上一層即天台位置，檢查地面及結構安全是否有問題。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062974/即時-港聞-大角咀中英樓單位塌石屎天花-女戶主-中頭獎-淌血送院",
