        {
            "title": "盧瀚霆Anson Lo與名設計師合作推出日常穿搭單品與神徒聯繫 預告年底個唱破格騷肌 拍杜琪峯新戲望對方鬧學習更多",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"盧瀚霆Anson Lo與名設計師合作推出日常穿搭單品與神徒聯繫 預告年底個唱破格騷肌 拍杜琪峯新戲望對方鬧學習更多\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/09eaae1827aea05156320b5b96b8214d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040913490894457.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">盧瀚霆Anson Lo與名設計師合作推出日常穿搭單品與神徒聯繫 預告年底個唱破格騷肌 拍杜琪峯新戲望對方鬧學習更多</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>盧瀚霆（Anson Lo）與意大利著名設計師Giuseppe Zanotti今日（9日）現身尖沙咀，出席《Giuseppe x Anson Lo》獨家聯名膠囊系列發布活動，吸引大批粉絲到場。Anson Lo表示設計了手提袋、皮革騎士靴和運動鞋，以他標誌性的粉紅色、生日日期和喜愛的玫瑰金色調作為設計元素，花了大約3個月時間設計，坦言設計上有難度，最初本想以破格的設計，但太前衛又不配襯他日常穿搭，所以設計可日常穿搭的單品能與神徒聯繫。\n\n</p><h2>Anson Lo談年底個唱</h2>\n<p>Anson Lo又稱一向對設計有熱誠，是次合作令他對鞋履有更多認識，大讚Giuseppe Zanotti非常友善，有熱誠和幹勁，像慈父般關懷別人。他表示最初與時尚界大人物合作很驚，以為對方很嚴肅，早前首次網上會議見對方常講笑，又有留意他的穿搭，首日會議令他感到驚喜又輕鬆。談到年底個人演唱會，Anson Lo表示向來在服裝上都會給予意見，要過到自己個關，更透露這次演唱會較破格，會鍛練身形，他說︰「每次MIRROR演唱會我都會露少少肌肉，今次睇吓有咩露嘅方法。（展示未露過的部位？）maybe，呢次演唱會主題好特別。」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3444831/Chill-Club%E9%A0%92%E7%8D%8E%E7%A6%AE2025MIRROR%E8%88%87Kelly%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%B0%E5%8B%81%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83-AL%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C%E9%9B%B6%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%81%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93-%E5%A7%9C%E6%BF%A46%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%97%E5%BE%97%E7%8D%8E%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E5%BF%83\">Chill Club頒獎禮2025｜MIRROR與Kelly同台勁開心 AL回應新歌零宣傳被指遭公司打壓 姜濤6個字得獎感受全是真心</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185161/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo今日出席活動，一出場見神徒即打招呼派心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/537599d13e44bf698b5b452848350b9b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_19_52.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo今日出席活動，一出場見神徒即打招呼派心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185163/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo與意大利著名設計師Giuseppe Zanotti今日現身尖沙咀，出席聯名膠囊系列發布活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d873773046f24acf705a447deda06ff/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_17.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo與意大利著名設計師Giuseppe Zanotti今日現身尖沙咀，出席聯名膠囊系列發布活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185166/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo與Giuseppe Zanotti攬攬預祝對方生日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c9217d1ba38dbac02ecd9870c6663788/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_25.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo與Giuseppe Zanotti攬攬預祝對方生日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185186/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日前Chill-Club頒獎禮2025，Anson Lo囊括「年度男歌手」金獎、「人人樂壇年度歌手大獎」、「人人樂壇年度歌曲大獎」。  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d9faef917293ff887edddc116ecad369/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-07_at_12_56_44_AM_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日前Chill-Club頒獎禮2025，Anson Lo囊括「年度男歌手」金獎、「人人樂壇年度歌手大獎」、「人人樂壇年度歌曲大獎」。  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185187/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日前MIRROR再度奪得「Chill Club年度組合」金獎。 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f45fc3fa9e01c9304a723ce12821f8b3/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-07_at_12_56_35_AM_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日前MIRROR再度奪得「Chill Club年度組合」金獎。 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185168/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo表示設計了手提袋、皮革騎士靴等，以他標誌性的粉紅色、生日日期和玫瑰金色調作為設計元素。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33dfd8baf154e1378ec6a33e8eb9aac5/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_27.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo表示設計了手提袋、皮革騎士靴等，以他標誌性的粉紅色、生日日期和玫瑰金色調作為設計元素。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185170/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo花了大約3個月時間設計可日常穿搭的單品，與神徒聯繫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e588a5094b5cddccc39c3694954c2f76/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_29.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo花了大約3個月時間設計可日常穿搭的單品，與神徒聯繫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185172/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo未開工拍攝新劇《The Season》，亦未有訓練戲中歌舞環節。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62ae296f3fa2dabcac6d4561089e57ab/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_31_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo未開工拍攝新劇《The Season》，亦未有訓練戲中歌舞環節。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185173/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo說《The Season》以他所知與木村光希沒對手戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4461f58dc6fa5721dda2c56870f76607/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_31.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo說《The Season》以他所知與木村光希沒對手戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185174/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"杜琪峯新戲談「希望」，Anson Lo指有很多層次，他要繼續拍才了解當中意思。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0164d292eaf3fde5cb51f8e96f9c497b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_32_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        杜琪峯新戲談「希望」，Anson Lo指有很多層次，他要繼續拍才了解當中意思。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185175/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo談到與杜琪峯合作的新戲僅拍了10日便停工，他說已預留檔期作好準備。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a8c70315ebd4213cce44eec79553ad67/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_32.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo談到與杜琪峯合作的新戲僅拍了10日便停工，他說已預留檔期作好準備。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185179/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"神徒聲勢浩大！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/008b40606d4fde19e7e0788b1a0b7058/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_34_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神徒聲勢浩大！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185181/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Anson Lo的大批支持者好早嚟霸位見偶像。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/12fdd0d1e1681331716b3c5a49ad130b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_35_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Anson Lo的大批支持者好早嚟霸位見偶像。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185182/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"神徒逼滿商場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/400cf84effb785d0a3320c4f5360ee87/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_12_20_35.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        神徒逼滿商場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>Anson Lo拍戲拍劇勁忙</h2>\n<p>談到杜琪峯表示與他合作的新戲僅拍了10日便停工，會趕快完成。Anson Lo表示也希望快完成，暫未收通知何時再開工，他已預留檔期作好準備。問有否打亂他的工作？他說沒有，很早之前接拍該片及預留檔期，與其他工作沒有衝突。提到杜Sir透露新戲以「希望」為主題，他指杜Sir的「希望」不是那麼表面，是很多層次，他仍未了解對方的意思，要再繼續拍才知。是否要再重新投入演出狀態？他說是，自己只拍了4組，對白不多，他說︰「杜Sir要我好focus狀態，盡量自然唔好浮誇。係難㗎，要求好高，嗰4組我知道咗到好多嘢。眼神嘅多與少，拿捏嘅程度，唔可以話學到，係領略到個concept。（是否擔心交不到戲？）擔心，每個take已盡力，都順利，最多NG 3次。」他又稱杜Sir對他沒讚沒鬧，他沒期望讚，反而期望對方鬧他，可以學習更多，不用特別令他feel good。另外，Anson Lo表示自己尚未開工拍攝新劇《The Season》，亦暫未訓練戲中歌舞環節，等待劇組通知，以他所知與木村光希沒對手戲。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
